<DocsLayout title="存储后端" description="在 PicFast 中配置存储后端。">
  <h1>存储后端</h1>
  <p>PicFast 支持多种存储后端，通过后台管理界面进行配置。</p>

  <h2>本地存储</h2>
  <p>将文件存储在本地文件系统。最简单的方案，适合单服务器部署。</p>
  <pre><code>{'{'}#123;
  "type": "local",
  "root": "/data/uploads",
  "url": "https://pics.example.com/uploads"
{'}'}#125;</code></pre>

  <h2>S3 兼容存储</h2>
  <p>支持 AWS S3、MinIO、Cloudflare R2 等 S3 兼容对象存储服务。</p>
  <pre><code>{'{'}#123;
  "type": "s3",
  "endpoint": "https://s3.us-east-1.amazonaws.com",
  "region": "us-east-1",
  "bucket": "my-picfast",
  "access_key": "AKIAIOSFODNN7EXAMPLE",
  "secret_key": "wJalrXUtnFEMI/K7MDENG/bPxRfiCYEXAMPLEKEY",
  "url": "https://my-picfast.s3.us-east-1.amazonaws.com"
{'}'}#125;</code></pre>

  <h2>阿里云 OSS</h2>
  <pre><code>{'{'}#123;
  "type": "oss",
  "endpoint": "oss-cn-hangzhou.aliyuncs.com",
  "bucket": "my-picfast",
  "access_key": "your-access-key",
  "secret_key": "your-secret-key",
  "url": "https://my-picfast.oss-cn-hangzhou.aliyuncs.com"
{'}'}#125;</code></pre>

  <h2>腾讯云 COS</h2>
  <pre><code>{'{'}#123;
  "type": "cos",
  "bucket_url": "https://my-picfast.cos.ap-guangzhou.myqcloud.com",
  "secret_id": "your-secret-id",
  "secret_key": "your-secret-key",
  "url": "https://my-picfast.cos.ap-guangzhou.myqcloud.com"
{'}'}#125;</code></pre>

  <h2>七牛云 Kodo</h2>
  <pre><code>{'{'}#123;
  "type": "kodo",
  "access_key": "your-access-key",
  "secret_key": "your-secret-key",
  "bucket": "my-picfast",
  "domain": "https://pics.example.com",
  "zone": "zone0"
{'}'}#125;</code></pre>

  <h2>WebDAV</h2>
  <pre><code>{'{'}#123;
  "type": "webdav",
  "endpoint": "https://dav.example.com",
  "username": "user",
  "password": "password",
  "url": "https://dav.example.com/pics"
{'}'}#125;</code></pre>

  <h2>切换后端</h2>
  <p>已存储在某个后端的图片不受影响。切换默认后端后，新上传的图片会写入新后端，已有图片继续从原位置提供访问。</p>
</DocsLayout>
